  "body": "In https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/v0.8.3/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#int_to_bytes\r\n\r\nThe int_to_bytes and bytes_to_int depend on Python implementation of to_bytes\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndef int_to_bytes(n: uint64, length: uint64) -> bytes:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Return the ``length``-byte serialization of ``n``.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    return n.to_bytes(length, ENDIANNESS)\r\n```\r\n\r\nA description of what this method does should be added so that we don't have to look into the Python spec.",
